international airport 24 hours ahead of the soviet leader 
scheduled arrival it will accompany gorbachev throughout his trip 
this week to new york havana and london 
the caviar was black russian and better than the fare usually 
found at 30000 feet but the inaugural flight of glasnost one 
named after gorbachevs policy of openness had little else to 
