why evans ruled as she did to me shes wrong so youre asking 
the wrong person he saidjones he said is a pretty strong 
man he thinks hes right and wants to pursue the appeal 
aids or acquired immune deficiency syndrome cripples the bodys 
immune system leaving a person prey to deadly cancers and other 
infections 
