saufley field is a naval training systems center that provides 
logistical and engineering support services for navy and marine 
training no aircraft are based there but its runways are used for 
landing and takeoff practice by training aircraft from whiting 
field near milton 
the prison renovation began in june when 15 inmates were brought 
to saufley from the federal prison at eglin air force base about 40 
miles away and the work force was increased to its present level 
last month said prison superintendent mark henry 
